OPERATING LOSS FOR FISCAL 2003 WAS FLAT WITH THE PRIOR YEAR AS HIGHER MARKETING EXPENSES AND HEADCOUNT-RELATED COSTS ASSOCIATED WITH PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT OFFSET THE GROWTH IN REVENUE. PRIOR YEAR REVENUE AND OPERATING LOSS FOR MOBILE AND EMBEDDED

