WITH THE UNDERLYING PERFORMANCE OF SUCH ENTITIES. THE INCREASE IN LOSSES ON EQUITY INVESTEES AND OTHER IN FISCAL 2001 REFLECTED AN INCREASE IN THE NUMBER OF SUCH INVESTMENTS DURING THE YEAR.

