CHARACTERISTICS OF BOTH LIABILITIES AND EQUITY. IT REQUIRES THAT AN ISSUER CLASSIFY A FINANCIAL INSTRUMENT THAT IS WITHIN ITS SCOPE AS A LIABILITY (OR AN ASSET IN SOME

